  "response": "There are several songs titled \"Home\" by different artists. Some notable ones include:\n\n1. **Michael Bubl\u00e9** - His song \"Home\" is a popular ballad that expresses longing for loved ones.\n2. **Edward Sharpe and the Magnetic Zeros** - Their song \"Home\" is an indie folk anthem about love and belonging.\n3. **Daughtry** - The rock band Daughtry has a song called \"Home\" that talks about returning to loved ones.\n4. **Phillip Phillips** - He has a well-known song titled \"Home\" that was released as his debut single after winning \"American Idol.\"\n\nIf you have a specific artist or genre in mind, please provide more details!",
